Package: hazmat
Type: Package
Title: Identify Hazardous Materials In R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ryan", "Thomas", email = "rthomas2003@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The goal of hazmat is to provide a simple way for educators, and 
    other folks that need to run a lot of other people’s code, to have some 
    confidence that there aren’t any unexpected scary R snippets.
